#comment: Lawn now features an extension via 5 planks and new starting layout. You start with extra sun and your plants are planted in columns however your seedpackets recharge slower, you don't get any sun from the sky and get no shovel. On top of that you get special seedbank that removes all sun producers, most splash plants and plants that generally would benefit from CLYSE rule too much. Zombie density is severely increased. All Surfer Zombies were removed in favour of Excavators. Added Barrelroller Bros, Mechanics, Punks, Lunar Dancers, Elite Prospectors, Elite Captains, Elite Shield Zombies and Elite Turquoise Skulls as well as a few surprises along the way | Veteran changes: added molds on c1 and c6. Added a few Sloth Gargantuars along the level. May the bread be with you

objdata.Name: Hot Sauce Challenge - Double Deck Power Trip

objdata.Description:
Survive with a special seed bank while plants recharge slower but planted in columns
Survive while sun doesn't drop from the sky and you don't have access to the shovel
